				SNiPA is a joint project of the <a href="http://www.helmholtz-muenchen.de/en/ibis/" target="_blank">Institute of Bioinformatics and Systems Biology</a> (IBIS) at the  <a href="http://www.helmholtz-muenchen.de" target="_blank">Helmholtz Zentrum M&uuml;nchen</a> and the <a href="http://qatar-weill.cornell.edu/research/faculty/suhreLab.html" target="_blank">Bioinformatics Core Facility</a> at the <a href="http://qatar-weill.cornell.edu" target="_blank">Weill Cornell Medical College in Qatar</a>.<br /><br />
